    "description": "<strong>以自己的方式探索Arcadia。拯救你的好友。时间正在流逝。</strong><br><br>Alma是一个机器人，在与人类的战争后醒来，发现世界已处于废墟之中。Anima，一种赋予机器人感知的资源，正在耗尽，并将Alma的好友变成无意识的杀人机器：UNSIGHTED。<br><br><strong>主要特点：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>以自己的方式探索：</strong>Arcadia的世界广阔无比，正适合探索，而且有许多捷径以及世界表面和地底的地图，让您去发现。当一条路径看起来太棘手时，试着为熟悉的武器和工具寻找新用途。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/e040fc7ef1a1bd34977223bdc27445f3.poster.avif?t=1709409664\" width=506 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/e040fc7ef1a1bd34977223bdc27445f3.webm?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/e040fc7ef1a1bd34977223bdc27445f3.mp4?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>丰富多样的战斗：</strong>打造适合您游戏风格的完美装备。《UNSIGHTED》允许玩家以各种方式装备武器，包括双持剑，以及手里剑和霰弹枪的组合。Alma将需要使用完美精确的战斗动作来触发更快的装填速度，或使用大规模破坏性的招架以在城市中生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/9d00c13687d5e61a75571bfe63f9b9f1.poster.avif?t=1709409664\" width=506 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/9d00c13687d5e61a75571bfe63f9b9f1.webm?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/9d00c13687d5e61a75571bfe63f9b9f1.mp4?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>制作和升级：</strong>在您的旅途中您将发现芯片；使用它们并通过广泛的升级树来升级Alma。您可以制作或发现新芯片，而且每个芯片都提供不同的加成效果。尝试构建几乎无限的角色成长系统，包括快速高效的，以及强大而充满风格的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/ad456a09db82dda3c3fe70cda2850782.poster.avif?t=1709409664\" width=504 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/ad456a09db82dda3c3fe70cda2850782.webm?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/ad456a09db82dda3c3fe70cda2850782.mp4?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>您的选择尤其重要：</strong>Alma枯萎的生命力随实时流逝，并且是《UNSIGHTED》剧情的驱动因素。在一个地方逗留太久，你可能会发现关键NPC在你遇到他们之前已变成了Unsighted。为了自己的生存，保存或耗尽其他机器人的Anima。时间的不断流逝会导致截然不同的结局，让您的重玩保持新鲜和令人有所期待。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/251eaf2db1dfccfccffd5b5cc5ce32a1.poster.avif?t=1709409664\" width=504 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/251eaf2db1dfccfccffd5b5cc5ce32a1.webm?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/251eaf2db1dfccfccffd5b5cc5ce32a1.mp4?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>高度可重玩 + 合作模式：</strong>除了主线故事，《UNSIGHTED》还具有额外的挑战模式，头目狂潮和地牢突袭。您还可以通过功能齐全的合作模式带好友一起穿越Arcadia。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/4755f02701487ca67666e4ca0c747c2a.poster.avif?t=1709409664\" width=506 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/4755f02701487ca67666e4ca0c747c2a.webm?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1062110/extras/4755f02701487ca67666e4ca0c747c2a.mp4?t=1709409664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
